fields.name: internal-ipv6
fields.description: The Internal IPV6 profile binds to the IP version 6 address and is similar to the Internal profile.

fields.name: external-ipv6
fields.description: The External IPV6 profile binds to the IP version 6 address and is similar to the External profile.

fields.name: external
fields.description: The External profile external provides anonymous calling in the public context. By default the External profile binds to port 5080. Calls can be sent using a SIP URL:voip.domain.com:5080

fields.name: internal
fields.description: The Internal profile by default requires registration which is used by the endpoints. By default the Internal profile binds to port 5060.
